             (police-constable G 162). I was sent for to the prosecutor's house - I found the prisoner there - he said to the prosecutor, "I thought you agreed to take 3s. a week" - the prosecutor said, "No, I will give you in charge" - and in going along, he said, two or three times, he would give 3s. a week.</p>
